Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.84,0:11:45.13,辉英,,0,0,0,,You can improve your skills while in a tram, walking
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.84,0:11:45.13,辉中,,0,0,0,,给Brilliant挤几滴
