Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.13,0:11:47.46,辉中,,0,0,0,,bro的大脑就能LEVEL UP
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.46,0:11:48.79,辉英,,0,0,0,,We personally love the app.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.46,0:11:48.79,辉中,,0,0,0,,我们私下很喜欢这款APP
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.79,0:11:50.76,辉英,,0,0,0,,There's something incredibly satisfying
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.79,0:11:50.76,辉中,,0,0,0,,学到真芝士
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.76,0:11:52.16,辉英,,0,0,0,,about really getting something
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.76,0:11:52.16,辉中,,0,0,0,,还有解出高考最后一题
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.16,0:11:54.62,辉英,,0,0,0,,about solving puzzle or logic problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.16,0:11:54.62,辉中,,0,0,0,,所带来的满足感是无与伦比的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.62,0:11:55.64,辉英,,0,0,0,,Why don't you give it a try.
